metadata.name: Dance of Spring
metadata.description:
Dance of Spring
春之舞
3543x2724px 300dpi PNG
Digital Illustration

In Spring time, the cherry blossom started to fly around, giving the forest the most beautiful spectacle. That’s the moment the Itsuki gets busy preparing for the future, protecting the forest and its new borns, and helping the trees to root. The whole scene they call it <Dance of Spring>, the most important celebration of the year. 

This is an Itsuki Fan Art based on Itsuki #5426.
